ICO.Description:
StockBet is a platform that provides social competition on stock betting. The Stockbet token is based on the Ethereum blockchain and is used to bet on the platform.  StockBet has already built software that is in use.

The StockBet ICO will start on the 29th of October. The ICO token allocation represents 70% of the total token supply which will be defined during the ICO, according to the funds raised. There is an hidden cap for the StockBet ICO and the starting price is 0.0001 ETH

Token Reserve Split:

  • 10% for founders,
  • 7% for team members,
  • 5% for investors,
  • 5% for bounties,
  • 2% for creditors
